title: IAA Tonight | The New York Jets Keep Winning! AND The World Series is Set.
description: Matt Ryan has officially been benched in favor of backup QB Sam Ehlinger. Should Matty Ice, the former MVP, hang 'em up? Also, Douz's Jets are on a roll but star rookie Breece Hall is out for the season with a torn ACL, however a new reinforcement is on the way. Also, the Phillies and Astros are headed to the Worlds Series. We give you a quick preview of how things might turnout.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Omar KElly, Adam Pacman Jones)
